Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Input files", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8824431277974443`*^9, 
  3.882443129698139*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b3741e50-12a2-4e3c-998f-\
4ccdfba893d3"],

Cell["\<\
Pdb and itp files of monomer fragments are used to build the molecule itp and \
gro files. 
Monomer itp and pdb files are stored in this section as tables.
Pdb files were optimized in gaussian prior to importing here. 
Format follows hetatm format: \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]HETATM\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] serial# atomname residuename residue# (always 1) \
Xcoord Ycoord Zcoord(~0 for rings) element
  https://www.wwpdb.org/documentation/file-format-content/format33/sect9.html\
\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.883228844558695*^9, 3.883228895835186*^9}, {
   3.883228933993925*^9, 3.883229098589328*^9}, {3.88322958452391*^9, 
