   3.985358670957301*^9},ExpressionUUID->"80c00c5e-0207-45fe-85e8-\
bb7bbb388089"],

Cell["\<\
Make sure the imported files are calling the proper directory.
Note that atoms in pdb and itp monomers should match .\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9853586779111223`*^9, 
  3.9853586933419857`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3f530629-775f-4d77-9bd6-\
