Cell["\<\
getPDBInfo selects relevant sections of the pdb table. Requires a pdb file \
that has been imported as a table from the input file section. Outputs a list \
(of lists):
getPDBInfo[[1]] is a list of the coordinates of each atom in the monomer, \
standardized to nanometers
getPDBInfo[[2]] is a list of atom names in the monomer
getPDBInfo[[3]] is a list of the conects, (the chemical bonds of the monomer)
getPDBInfo[[4]] is the residue name of the monomer
getPDBInfo[[5]] is a list of elements\
\>", "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.88322923565079*^9, 3.883229427152525*^9}, {
  3.88322946315021*^9, 3.883229496989978*^9}, {3.883229532516529*^9, 
